<i>adjective</i>: 원만하다 [원만하다], 순탄하다 [순ː탄하다], 수더분하다 [수더분하다], 선하다 [선ː하다], 선량하다 [설ː량하다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>원만하다 [원만하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. mild; good-tempered; good-natured</dd><br>
<dd>성격이 부드럽고 너그럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's personality being gentle and generous.</dd><br>
<dd>2. smooth; peaceful</dd><br>
<dd>일의 진행이 순조롭다.</dd><br>
<dd>The progress of something being smooth.</dd><br>
<dd>3. friendly; intimate</dd><br>
<dd>서로 사이가 좋다.</dd><br>
<dd>Getting along well with each other.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>순탄하다 [순ː탄하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. good-natured; fair</dd><br>
<dd>성질이 까다롭지 않다.</dd><br>
<dd>The personality of someone not being fussy.</dd><br>
<dd>2. smooth</dd><br>
<dd>길이 험하지 않고 평탄하다.</dd><br>
<dd>The road not being rough but being smooth.</dd><br>
<dd>3. smooth</dd><br>
<dd>삶이나 과정 등이 문제없이 순조롭다.</dd><br>
<dd>The process of something, the life of someone, etc., being smooth without any problems.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>수더분하다 [수더분하다]</dt><br>
<dd>good-natured; good-tempered; gentle</dd><br>
<dd>성질이 까다롭지 않고 순하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Meek, not fastidious.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>선하다 [선ː하다]</dt><br>
<dd>nice; good-natured</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 행동이 올바르고 착하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's mind or behavior being right and good.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>선량하다 [설ː량하다]</dt><br>
<dd>virtuous; good-natured</dd><br>
<dd>성품이나 행실이 어질고 착하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's personality or behavior being gracious and good.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>